       (tires screeching)

65
00:02:36.323 --> 00:02:37.589
      Hey. I'm-I'm sorry.

66
00:02:37.591 --> 00:02:39.324
        Yeah. some drunk
     and he almost hit me.

67
00:02:39.326 --> 00:02:40.692
        No. no. no. no.
      I'm fine. I'm fine.

68
00:02:40.694 --> 00:02:42.427
        I guess the bars
      must be letting out.

69
00:02:45.566 --> 00:02:47.933
    (crossing bell clanging)

70
00:02:55.609 --> 00:02:57.309
         What the hell?

71
