        you had an angel
  looking out for you tonight.

83
00:04:21.695 --> 00:04:23.495
You said
you knew this guy.

84
00:04:23.497 --> 00:04:24.763
               I was an admirer.

85
00:04:24.765 --> 00:04:27.299
                   Garrison Boyd
                   was president

86
